Woot!

One of the other designers here gave me durian candy.

I'm scared to eat it, even though durian's good when you get past the stinkiness!

I am a photoshop fucking NINJA!


*hyah*

In a quest to quit smoking at the busiest time of year here, I bought a nicotine patch.

There is no way that I can function with that thing slapped to my arm.  It made me dizzy and nauseous and now my chest hurts a little.  But it's slowly going away.

so drunk/.


Deeeee-runk!


Awww.  Yeah.

Win count: Zilch.

My first rimming of the season, up it rolls......aaaannnnddd....


...please play again.

Gargh!

(Yes, I thought out how that sounded.  I know how it sounded.  Comments on how it sounded?  Not so necessary :P)

So my vet called me last night to inform me that Bacon has gingivitis.  I have to brush his teeth on a regular basis with chicken-flavoured toothpaste.  Poor little dude.  His gums are all inflamed.  And there is nothing that makes you feel more guilty than being called to say that you've been both feeding him kitten food for too long, and that it could be genetic but eventually, if you don't brush his teeth every day, he'll need his teeth out.  Gargh.

So supposedly I won a two for the price of one on an Olivia cruise.  Hahahahaha.  I wonder how many people scored that.  Though it would kick ass.


hahaha.
I need a shopping opinion buddy.  Anyone game?
